      "content": "i dont know about hope. it just feels like i'm a ghost haunting my own life. like there's this heavy, physical thing that's still walking around and eating and breathing, but the 'me' part is just... gone. it feels so pointless to keep dragging this empty vessel around when there's no more art, no more color, nothing. why should the vessel stay if the essence is dead?",
